; [Name]
; Level= What level can the player use this ability at?
; Type= attack/Buff/heal/scriptonly
; AOE= true/false
; Info= Desc shown in !view-info
; Description= What shows when this is used in battle
; Cooldown=# how many turns do you have to wait to use this one again
; Cost=how much TP does it cost to use?
; Potency= the potency amount for attack type
; Stat= What stat does this ability check when calculating damage?
; EnmityMultiplier=How much enmity will this ability generate? For example 2 = 2*damage, 5 = 5*damage
; Job= which jobs can use this ability?
; StatusEffect= Which status effect is applied to the target?
; CanUseOutsideBattle= true/false  If true then it can be used in adventures outside of battle

